				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">A Primer on India&#8217;s Parliamentary Elections</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Malavika Vyawahare			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-04-08T04:20:09+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">April 8, 2014 12:20 am</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">April 8, 2014 12:20 am</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div class="w592"><figure class="promo media video blog-video "
    data-videoid="100000002825241" data-media-action="modal" data-autoplay="" data-embedded="true" aria-label="media" role="group">
